column1: Daily Weather Observations for Adelaide, South Australia for November 2012
Prepared at 13:05 UTC on Friday  9 August 2013   IDCJDW5002.201211
Observations are from Kent Town, about 2 km east of the city centre.
Kent Town is a suburban site with good exposure. Climate averages are available for West Terrace as well as Kent Town.
Observations were drawn from Adelaide (Kent Town) {station 023090}
